cs.NI, cs.IT, cs.MM, cs.SY, cs.CR

This paper discusses the performance analysis of cellular networks, which involves network connectivity and user mobility. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture). The paper also discusses statistical properties and analytical approaches, which are related to information theory (cs.IT) and multimedia (cs.MM). The paper also mentions challenges associated with mobility-aware analysis, which is related to system and control (cs.SY) and cryptography and security (cs.CR).
